data.description: Back on market!  Buyers financing was delayed.  Great opportunity for affordable living in Fruita.  Nice size double wide home on one of the largest lots in Holly Park. The perk of this park is the homeowner owns the land, so no lot rent!  This home is on a corner lot and has parking on both sides, including plentiful RV parking and a large shed for storage.  The yard is a blank slate for a beautiful yard, gardens or just a secure area for your furry friends.  If privacy is what you desire, there is a split floor plan and an office.  Schedule a showing today.  Affordable homes like this one don't appear often!  The house could use some TLC and is priced accordingly and being sold as-is.
